    {
        "content": "<p>You were omitting two many parentheses (<code>hom_dagger ùüô x</code> instead of <code>hom_dagger (ùüô x)</code>, <code>hom_dagger x ‚Üí y</code> instead of <code>hom_dagger (x ‚Üí y)</code>), and you didn't make <code>x</code> and <code>y</code> implicit in <code>hom_dagger</code> so you were bound to get an error when not providing <code>x</code> and <code>y</code> (for example you would need to write <code>hom_dagger x x (ùüô x)</code>).</p>",
