span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">dagger_category.hom_dagger</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">map</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Thanks again</p>",
